TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_DEMAND_UNITS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT PRIMARY_DC, STYLE_NUM, STYLE_SUF, COLOR_CODE, COLOR_SUF, PUT_UP_CODE, PACK_CODE, SIZE_DESC, SUM(OPEN_ORDER_GARMENTS/DECODE(HISTORICAL_BUSINESS_UNIT,'UW',(CASE WHEN ASCII(PACK_CODE)>=65 THEN ASCII(PACK_CODE)-55 WHEN PACK_CODE LIKE 'X' THEN 1 ELSE TO_NUMBER(PACK_CODE) END),decode(pack_code,'X',1,to_number(pack_code)))) DEMAND_ORDER_UNITS FROM OPEN_ORDER_DC_OVERFLOW GROUP BY PRIMARY_DC, STYLE_NUM, STYLE_SUF, COLOR_CODE, COLOR_SUF, PUT_UP_CODE, PACK_CODE, SIZE_DESC
